{"type": "article", "id": 3862, "title": "Geometry 系列餐具", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-26T07:30:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233039TsdtJzaAFLlwCeHR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t伦敦设计工作室 DesignK 的创始人 Byung 日前推出了一套名为「Geometry Collection」的餐具，其灵感来源于德国艺术家奥斯卡·施莱默( Oskar Schlemmer )创作的芭蕾舞剧「Triadisches Ballett」，设计出来的餐具的几何形状也极具受包豪斯影响的现代主义设计风格，线条与圆形球体的结合在 Byung 手中变成了餐具的手柄与盖子。Geometry Collection 包含有一个咖啡杯、一个碟子、一个水杯、一个糖罐以及牛奶罐。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233038YJ7CI9aoyBPg5cGM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233038LNMTeXb3DQc0wJEy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233039wETvrlhYc42qZPAd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}